### Get all professionals
GET http://localhost:8080/professionals

### Get a single professional (example: id 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/professionals/1

### Create a new professional
POST http://localhost:8080/professionals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "David Parker",
  "title": "Full Stack Developer",
  "bio": "Loves building both frontend and backend applications."
}

### Update a professional (example: id 2)
PUT http://localhost:8080/professionals/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Brian Lee",
  "title": "Senior Backend Engineer",
  "bio": "Now focuses on scalable microservices."
}

### Delete a professional (example: id 3)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/professionals/3
